{"tid":283219,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔中冇流血佢功勞？  梁特專訪稱指示警隊暫不清場","createTime":"2017-06-14T03:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T04:25:22.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84a47b8df6921890831726dbe05f679cc4b40539","tid":283219,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170614/large/1497411524_098f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170614%2Flarge%2F1497411524_098f.jpg&h=2b6ca282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還有約兩星期便卸任的行政長官梁振英接受中資的鳳凰衛視專訪，首度披露他處理2014年佔領運動的殺手鐧「就是忍，不採取行動」。他又代下屆特首林鄭月娥預告，未來五年都沒有重啟政改的基礎。 <br />\n<br />\n梁振英接受鳳凰衛視《問答神州》節目吳小莉專訪。據鳳凰衛視發出的新聞稿，梁振英首度披露在2014年處理佔領運動的策略，「就是忍，不採取行動」。 <br />\n2014年佔領運動歷時79天，當時建制派一面倒批評佔領者長期佔據道路，對社會及經濟造成影響。梁振英在訪問中首次承認，是他指示警方暫時不要清場。「警察的訓練就是處理這樣的場面的，你要警察不採取行動，要讓我們的警察同事們上上下下支持這個政策決定，給佔中的市民，給特區政府更多的時間，能夠讓雙方去談，這個是最困難的一個地方。」"},{"pid":"ebe7831b0ec0011806b1575e2cd1fc3b47f1d793","tid":283219,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:57:14.000Z","msg":"唔係你d催淚彈又點會有佔中"},{"pid":"c3ac852a37e94d9bd620c942298e16e41bfb006f","tid":283219,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"人唔笑"},{"pid":"469df6460d2d0d2684cd88a3b8045146aee9de51","tid":283219,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:57:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"829cb211a4b0017dba387cad02747252b762f96a","tid":283219,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"果然真係贏咗講乜都得"},{"pid":"874fb62bdb5a605b3388be6711e6e01af20da3f9","tid":283219,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"食屎狗"},{"pid":"14aca32fa837c89199e4a528de6b41b42e3b2cff","tid":283219,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"我淨係知689開完記者會之後黑警就準備屠城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20140929/large/29la1p100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140929%2Flarge%2F29la1p100.jpg&h=6de585a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a65840d53438cfd8b430a973939f6dbf2edbe1d","tid":283219,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20140930/large/1412068575_66b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140930%2Flarge%2F1412068575_66b9.jpg&h=8fc6d8a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c3067e3177fc4e0555a3b3fbb4532564fb30cb2","tid":283219,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:08:04.000Z","msg":"醫院管理局最新公布（只有中文）<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n下稿代醫院管理局發出︰<br />\n<br />\n　　醫院管理局發言人作以下公布：<br />\n<br />\n　　由於政府總部集會關係，本局預計有大量傷者需要送院接受治療。市民如有需要到港島區三間急症室（瑪麗醫院、律敦治及鄧肇堅醫院、東區尤德夫人那打素醫院）求診，輪候時間有機會較平日長，敬請耐心等候。<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n２０１４年９月２８日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間１８時４５分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201409/28/P201409280831.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201409%2F28%2FP201409280831.htm&d=fGBCbTgfTb2PkxpjPpctbVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=824d97bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201409/28/P201409280831.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/717/21646369415_abb1906edb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F717%2F21646369415_abb1906edb.jpg&h=50b45b6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2ed68f312786ac13121303648b9c9120985fbbb","tid":283219,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"唔用警察，用藍絲呀嘛"}]}